{"tid":1078139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平判刑】劉兆佳籲出獄後繼續服務國家","createTime":"2019-03-26T05:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T09:08:15.000Z","uid":30647,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b40b7dc13e7957b84e16ab7efb1c2395a2314548","tid":1078139,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有份為何志平撰寫求情信的全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳表示，按何志平的成就而言，無論判囚多久都是「相當重」的刑罰。劉承認法庭很可能是考慮到何志平的社會地位和醫學成就，加上何已年近70歲，出獄後重犯機會很低，故今次囚刑算是輕判，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">何最少不用在獄中度過餘生，出獄後仍有機會服務社會和國家</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他寄語何在獄中「多多保重、注重健康」，並持續學習和了解中、港和國際社會的發展</span></span>，認為外界大多會希望何出獄後繼續為不同組織擔任顧問等工作，以服務大眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190326/59412455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59412455&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhtTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=91f08f67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59412455&h=89c2a6e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190326/59412455</a>"},{"pid":"d31b5a31ed00d618e6cd164f61f7acda24842e21","tid":1078139,"uid":39200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"出獄後繼續為不同組織擔任顧問等工作<br />\n<br />\n做condom 出事又拉又坐過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef195e2ad4600e756daeb76b48634fa77c07b9ed","tid":1078139,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"仲敢唔敢番香港都成問題"},{"pid":"8dc4f693f2499abc931f75295b184ed57ddbf7f1","